Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those houses will drop on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think one of those houses... is Eren's?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eren's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is eavesdropping!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasha, could you smack Conny?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he knows our location.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's making Shiganshina a sea of flames\Nby scattering burning debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, you think you \Ncan burn down my city?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Armin! The fire! Your orders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're standing there shaking so much,\Nyou can't do a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean, can you take my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have no idea.... what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong reading Bertholdt,\Nand look where it got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean! You're better suited for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The river! Move to the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone aboard Eren! Conserve our gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At some point, we'll have to\Nget Bertholdt's attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but until then, don't let him see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right at reading situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm coming up empty\Nwith a plan to get us out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we're all counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Perfect Game"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done cleaning up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only small ones left\Nare the ones way at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, how will we take down the Beast Titan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's perfectly content sitting\Nway over there, not moving an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it seems he's a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like he's ever had balls to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll mop up the rest of the small ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Hange and the others avoid it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta hurry to that side and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one was a little bit high...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, leave it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the first pitch was a warm-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going for a perfect game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frontal bombardment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does the enemy have cannons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, there's a hundred of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! You're scaring the horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Titan's throwing boulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Levi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, retreat to \Nthe wall with the horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Stay outta the line of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stand up! You wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His throws have destroyed\Nthe front line of houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he keeps on throwing,\Neverything will get leveled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't have anywhere left to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't retreat to the \Nother side of the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colossal Titan is \Nalready heading this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spreading fire all along his path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposing we scale the wall to evade\Nthe stones, we'd have to leave the horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we retreat here, there's \Nno hope for victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Hange's group?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Eren all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the majority of them\Nwere caught in that explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been dealt a serious blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Beast Titan directed the small Titans\Nso our soldiers would group up in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, while engaging the small Titans,\NDirk Squad, Marlene Squad, and Klaus Squad
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were all wiped out by the bombardment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, our remaining forces\Nthis side of the gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...consists of you new Scout recruits,\NCaptain Levi, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erwin... Do you have any sort of plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yell at him, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Bertholdt get \Nany closer to the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That bastard's ignoring us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What now, Jean?! At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eren! Go stop his lanky legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still! How the hell\Nare we gonna defeat him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His gusts of hot steam make\Nour ODM gear useless! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think I know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, we've got \Nno choice but to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta figure out his weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it. You guys distract him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conny, your Thunder Spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armin, we need you to observe him from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So quit your moping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta believe there's a way to beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing more...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...than a big damn wretched oaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's shoving him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Eren! Knock him over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be some sort of way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Is that Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got himself flung on top of the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eren's not moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not dead! Focus on the monster at hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might have been pushing it too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we run at him without a plan,\Nthat's what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we can somehow turn the tables on him,\Nthis recovery operation, all of our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the future of humanity will be doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that, I'm not about to sit\Naround while we all get slaughtered!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know about Thunder Spears yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conny, Sasha, and I will distract him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikasa will strike in the opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, moron! I'll poke out your stupid eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You huge idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You massive pervert lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This distraction is so obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we nail him with a Thunder Spear...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hot steam even knocked\Naway the Thunder Spears!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conny!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Breathing it in burned my throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikasa! You're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. A bit of shrapnel from\Nthe Thunder Spears got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought of anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have any clues for a counterattack?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:24.97,Eyecatch1A,,0000,0000,0000,,"Information Available for Public Disclosure"\N"The Colossal Titan's Steam"\N"A Titan's special powers are produced by using its own body as a resource. In that way, it is thought the steam emitted by the Colossal Titan consumes muscle tissue and therefore must be finite."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Beast Titan has a good\Nguess where we're at.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place will look like a honeycomb soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're saying we've got no chance to\Ncounterattack, let's get ready to flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake Eren sprawled out up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ride him and flee with\Nas many people as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least we'll have some survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The horse got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Like it matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Scouts were insanely strong\Nand they died in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know as well as I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good is protecting horses...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when there's nobody \Nleft to ride them home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all made sense at one point...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If humanity just hid behind the walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd someday get slaughtered\Nby Titans out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody has to bite the bullet\Nand risk taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for others to not become victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we needed people to become\Nthe victims themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will be that brave soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was asked that, I actually\Nbelieved I could be that someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that being sent to my death...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would turn out to be so\Nutterly meaningless in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet almost everyone ends up\Nsaying the same thing as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I ever think that I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...somehow be different?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if whoever's left of the recruits\Nand Hange's group scatter on horses...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and try to make it home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By using them as a decoy,\Nyou guys could escape on Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Levi. What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm facing the Beast Titan.\NI'll draw him away--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you and Eren return\Nhome alive, there's still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the best we can\Nask for at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be perfectly honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt a single one of us\Nis making it back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, assuming we had no way to counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say that sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you keep your shitty mouth shut?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the plan goes well, you may be able\Nto take down the Beast Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it will take the recruits...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and myself to give our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, most of us will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's almost guaranteed\Nwe'll all be wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, we can stake our heroic\Ndeaths on a slim chance of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For this to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To ask these young ones to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would take an expert con man\Nand a whole slew of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do not lead the vanguard,\Nnone of them will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will die before anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without ever learning \Nwhat's in the basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I've done till now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was because I thought this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That someday, I could check if I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many times... I thought death\Nwould be so much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But always, the dream I shared with\Nmy father flashed through my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:17:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I'm close enough to the\Nanswers to reach out and grab them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Levi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see them? Our comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our comrades are looking at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to know what became\Nof the hearts they gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the fighting isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all just inside my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing more than a childish delusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've fought well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you \Nthat we've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making the choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on your dream and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lead the recruits straight into hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take down the Beast Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I figured they wouldn't\Nlie down and die, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A suicide charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I was thinking they\Ncould do better than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's those signal things...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! It's coming, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm announcing our final operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be doing a cavalry charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal: To rush the Beast Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we'll be making\Nourselves ideal targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll wait until he's ready to throw\Nand fire our smoke signals together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should reduce his accuracy somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're acting as a decoy,\NCaptain Levi will kill the Beast Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to go after him\Nwith just ODM gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's standing in an empty area.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not even a house or tree in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There happens to be a line of\Nobjects at just the right height.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sneak close using the Titans...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and assassinate the Beast Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing and waiting just means\Nwe'll be showered by more boulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we all... heading...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to our deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're gonna die anyways,\Nyou're saying it's better...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if we die fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... If we're gonna die anyways,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how we die,\Neven if it's disobeying orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it all means nothing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're precisely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what dreams or hopes you had...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how blessed a life you've lived...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all the same if \Nyou're shredded by rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will die someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean life is meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there even any meaning in our being born?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you say that of our fallen comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were they meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they weren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's us who gives meaning\Nto our comrade's lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave fallen! The anguished fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who will remember\Nthem... are us, the living!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We die trusting the living who follow\Nto find meaning in our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the sole method in which we\Ncan rebel against this cruel world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soldiers, rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soldiers, scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soldiers, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For friends who gave up their hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For friends who gave up their dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until everything burns out,\Nthey will continue running...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...inside the chaos and panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.92,0:23:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: "Hero."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:56.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hero"
